#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn7.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga "
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Ahiṃsakasutta "
msgstr "5. Harmless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.165, sc1
msgctxt "sn7.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.5:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Harmless went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.5:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said, "

msgctxt "sn7.5:1.4"
msgid "“ahiṃsakāhaṃ, bho gotama, ahiṃsakāhaṃ, bho gotamā”ti. "
msgstr "“I am Harmless, Master Gotama, I am Harmless!” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.353, sc2
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.1"
msgid "“Yathā nāmaṃ tathā cassa, "
msgstr "“If you were really like your name, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.2"
msgid "siyā kho tvaṃ ahiṃsako; "
msgstr "then you’d be Harmless. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.3"
msgid "Yo ca kāyena vācāya, "
msgstr "But a truly harmless person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.4"
msgid "manasā ca na hiṃsati; "
msgstr "does no harm by way of "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.5"
msgid "Sa ve ahiṃsako hoti, "
msgstr "body, speech, or mind; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.6"
msgid "yo paraṃ na vihiṃsatī”ti. "
msgstr "they don’t harm anyone else.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn7.5:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Harmless said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! …” … "

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.3"
msgid "abbhaññāsi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā ahiṃsakabhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja the Harmless became one of the perfected."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
